lead_paragraph: Sydney Wiese had 11 points, including two 3-pointers, and six assists and became the first player in Pac-12 history with 300 career made 3s as No. 22 Oregon State beat Arkansas-Pine Bluff 73-40 on Tuesday night.

headline.print_headline: Wiese Hits 300th 3-Pointer, No. 22 Oregon St Women Beat UAPB
